data.description: Welcome to your own private oasis in Kirksville, Missouri! This stunning 4 bed, 3.5 bath fiber optic smart home is nestled on 4.5 wooded acres, offering tranquility and privacy with modern convenience. The spacious layout provides plenty of room for comfortable living, while the abundance of storage space ensures all your belongings have a place. RV enthusiasts will appreciate the dedicated parking area, while the new landscaping enhances the natural beauty of the surroundings. This home is truly move-in ready, allowing you to start enjoying the peaceful setting right away. Don't miss your chance to make this serene retreat your own! Contact the listing agent, Elizabeth Gregory, eXp Realty for more information 660.621.2136, www.missourihomeandfarm.com
